<template>
  <button @click="fetchProfessors">Premi</button>
  <button @click="fetchCourses('pippo@gmail.com')">Premi2</button>
</template>

<script>
import axios from "axios";

export default {
  name: "AddTeachingsPage",
  data(){
    return{
      listOfProfessor : null,
      selectedProfessor : null,
    }
  },

  async created(){
    await this.fetchProfessors();
  },
  methods : {
    async fetchProfessors(){
      try {
        const response = await axios.get('ServletProfessorRequests',{params : {action : 'getProfessors'}})
        this.listOfProfessor = response.data;
        console.log(response.data);
      }catch (e){
        console.log(e.response)
      }
    },
    async fetchCourses(email){
      try {
        const response = await axios.get('ServletProfessorRequests',{params : {action : 'getCourses',professorEmail : email}});
        console.log(response.data);
      }catch (e){
        console.log(e.response)
      }
    }
  },
  computed : {

  }
}
</script>
